name: PACK 000
description:
First release of the Brazilian label SAMPLEADA, PACK000 was created during the first months of the pandemic of Covid-19 and carries the feelings that this period in history brought. Inspired by the sound of hip hop's golden age, it contains samples of 1970s recordings of Japanese Jazz artists such as Takashi Kokubo, Masabumi Kikuchi in partnership with Gill Evans, Takao Naoi and Shiho Yabuki.
A piece for lovers of Urban Music and Contemporary Beats.
Made in Brazil
